title: How to Get Rid of Depression
itunes:title: How to Get Rid of Depression
description:
Episode 558 - This may be one of the most important episodes that I haver ever made. According to the news, depression is on the rise but also according to the news, 61% of people diagnosed with depression are misdiagnosed. So what is it that everyone has? Well, that is what I am going to be diving into on this episode and I will be teaching how to get past that depression as well!
